I'm the lead systems designer at Monolith.

6
00:00:24,052 --> 00:00:25,413
I think we'll start off with a video

7
00:00:26,053 --> 00:00:28,155
that shows us a little of Shadow of War.

8
00:01:27,471 --> 00:01:34,055
All right, at Monolith, our recent products have been Shadow of Mordor and Shadow of War.

9
