And we are based in Kirkland, Washington.

10
00:01:38,897 --> 00:01:40,058
It's a great place to work.

11
00:01:40,338 --> 00:01:42,719
Here's a little pic of our office building.

12
00:01:43,139 --> 00:01:44,220
A little bit about myself.

13
00:01:44,300 --> 00:01:50,163
Before these two products, I worked on several others, some Lord of the Rings based.

14
00:01:50,943 --> 00:01:53,445
Before that, I was in children's games.

15
00:01:53,745 --> 00:01:54,305
I did several.

16
00:01:54,345 --> 00:01:55,326
Here are a few of them.

17
00:01:56,306 --> 00:02:00,832
And before children's games, I was designing in other industries.

18
00:02:01,252 --> 00:02:05,798
I did a little designing for test systems for the F-16,

19
