237
00:14:11,174 --> 00:14:14,795
and then he'll be just like all those other captains.

238
00:14:15,055 --> 00:14:16,095
And then of course you hunt him down

239
00:14:16,115 --> 00:14:17,435
and you have the option as a player

240
00:14:17,515 --> 00:14:19,036
to give him a death threat.

241
00:14:19,056 --> 00:14:19,736
And I'll explain that.

242
00:14:20,536 --> 00:14:21,656
It means you give him a warning.

243
00:14:21,716 --> 00:14:22,696
I'm coming for you.

244
00:14:22,756 --> 00:14:23,236
A message.

245
00:14:23,276 --> 00:14:23,597
And then he...

246
00:14:24,237 --> 00:14:26,080
he prepares and he gets stronger.

247
00:14:26,140 --> 00:14:26,921
Why would you ever do that?

248
00:14:26,941 --> 00:14:30,525
It's because when you do get him, your loot is way better.

249
00:14:30,986 --> 00:14:33,228
So then you meet the captain again, he insults you again,

250
00:14:33,248 --> 00:14:37,113
and then you finally, if you're lucky, defeat him.

251
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:41,701
A lot of times they give last words if they can,

252
00:14:42,502 --> 00:14:45,564
